Change the IP address in the above "ip_address" field (192.168.0.x, 1 &#60; x 
&#60; 255) and finally create c:\bin\resolv.cfg:

SEARCH DNS HOSTS SEQUENTIAL
NAMESERVER xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx
NAMESERVER yyy.yyy.yyy.yyy
</screen>
